<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Unbound — Break free from codependency</title>
  <%- metaPixelSnippet %>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300;1,9..40,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <%- themeCSS %>
  <style>
    :root {
      --warm-cream: #FAF7F2;
      --deep-sage: #3D5A47;
      --light-sage: #7A9E87;
      --soft-terracotta: #C4856A;
      --dark-text: #1A1A1A;
      --muted-text: #6B6B6B;
      --pale-sage: #E8F0EA;
      --warm-blush: #F2E6DF;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--warm-cream);
      color: var(--dark-text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* Nav */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 24px 48px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .logo {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .nav-tag {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--light-sage);
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      color: white;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: #2d4535; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 48px 60px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-text h1 {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    }
    .hero-text h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--soft-terracotta);
    }
    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      max-width: 440px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      color: white;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #2d4535; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* Hero visual */
    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      height: 420px;
    }
    .hero-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 48px rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.08);
    }
    .hero-card-main {
      position: absolute;
      top: 40px;
      left: 0;
      right: 80px;
    }
    .hero-card-float {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 0;
      left: 80px;
      background: var(--warm-blush);
      border: 1px solid rgba(196, 133, 106, 0.2);
    }
    .card-eyebrow {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--soft-terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .card-progress-bar {
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--pale-sage);
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .card-progress-fill {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      border-radius: 3px;
      width: 33%;
      transition: width 0.4s ease;
    }
    .card-progress-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
    }
    .card-lesson-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 0;
    }
    .card-lesson-dot {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .card-lesson-dot::after {
      content: '';
      width: 6px;
      height: 4px;
      border-left: 1.5px solid white;
      border-bottom: 1.5px solid white;
      transform: rotate(-45deg) translateY(-1px);
    }
    .card-lesson-dot.empty {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.25);
    }
    .card-lesson-dot.empty::after { display: none; }
    .card-lesson-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--dark-text); }
    .card-lesson-text.muted { color: var(--muted-text); }

    /* Sections */
    .section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 48px;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--soft-terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-sub {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      max-width: 540px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    /* Feature list */
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .feature {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px 28px 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.1);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      background: var(--pale-sage);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .feature h3 {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .feature p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* CTA section */
    .cta-section {
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      margin: 0 48px 80px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 72px 64px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      right: -80px;
      width: 320px;
      height: 320px;
      background: rgba(122, 158, 135, 0.15);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .cta-section p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: white;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 16px 36px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
      position: relative;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    .cta-counter {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      position: relative;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.1);
      padding: 32px 48px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
    }
    .footer-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
    }

    /* Email capture section */
    .email-capture-section {
      background: var(--warm-blush);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(196, 133, 106, 0.18);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 133, 106, 0.18);
      padding: 72px 48px;
    }
    .ec-inner {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .ec-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(196, 133, 106, 0.15);
      color: var(--soft-terracotta);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(196, 133, 106, 0.25);
    }
    .ec-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 38px);
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      letter-spacing: -0.8px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .ec-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .ec-form {}
    .ec-fields {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      max-width: 440px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .ec-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.2);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--dark-text);
      background: white;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .ec-input:focus { border-color: var(--deep-sage); }
    .ec-input::placeholder { color: #aaa; }
    .ec-submit {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .ec-submit:hover { background: #2d4535; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .ec-submit:disabled { opacity: 0.65; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
    .ec-error {
      color: #c0392b;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .ec-privacy {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      margin-top: 12px;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }
    .ec-success {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .ec-success-check {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--deep-sage);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .ec-success-msg {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .ec-success-msg a {
      color: var(--soft-terracotta);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* Social proof bar — sits below hero */
    .social-proof-bar {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: -20px auto 0;
      padding: 0 48px 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .spb-avatars {
      display: flex;
    }
    .spb-avatar {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid var(--warm-cream);
      background: var(--pale-sage);
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-left: -8px;
    }
    .spb-avatar:first-child { margin-left: 0; }
    .spb-avatar:nth-child(2) { background: var(--warm-blush); color: var(--soft-terracotta); }
    .spb-avatar:nth-child(3) { background: #E0EDE3; color: var(--deep-sage); }
    .spb-avatar:nth-child(4) { background: #F5DED4; color: #A0674F; }
    .spb-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .spb-text strong {
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Testimonials section */
    .testimonials-section {
      padding: 80px 48px 72px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .testimonials-header {
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }
    .testimonials-header .section-label { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .testimonials-header .section-title { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .testimonials-header .section-sub { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .testimonials-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px 28px 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.1);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
    }
    .testimonial-card::before {
      content: '\201C';
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      right: 24px;
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 48px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--pale-sage);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    .tc-before {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding-right: 36px;
    }
    .tc-shift {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }
    .tc-outcome {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--soft-terracotta);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: var(--warm-blush);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .tc-author {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(61, 90, 71, 0.08);
    }
    .tc-author-avatar {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--pale-sage);
      color: var(--deep-sage);
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .tc-author-avatar.alt { background: var(--warm-blush); color: var(--soft-terracotta); }
    .tc-author-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--dark-text);
    }
    .tc-author-detail {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
    }
    .testimonials-note {
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      opacity: 0.7;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      nav, .hero, .section, footer { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding-top: 48px; }
      .hero-visual { height: 280px; }
      .cta-section { margin: 0 20px 60px; padding: 48px 32px; }
      .hero-card-main { right: 20px; }
      .hero-card-float { left: 20px; }
      .email-capture-section { padding: 56px 20px; }
      .social-proof-bar { padding: 0 20px 32px; margin-top: -8px; }
      .testimonials-section { padding: 56px 20px; }
      .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <span class="logo">Unbound</span>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;">
      <a href="/reset" class="nav-tag" style="text-decoration:none;">5-Minute Reset</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="nav-tag" style="text-decoration:none;">Blog</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="nav-tag" style="text-decoration:none;">Pricing</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/learn" class="nav-cta">Start the course</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>The real reason you <em>can't stop people-pleasing</em></h1>
      <p>Not a personality flaw. A neural pathway. One that can be rewired. Unbound is the course that shows you how.</p>
      <a href="/learn" class="hero-cta">
        Begin Module 1
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
          <path d="M3 8h10M8 3l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-card hero-card-main">
        <div class="card-eyebrow">Module 1 Progress</div>
        <div class="card-title">Recognizing the Pattern</div>
        <div class="card-progress-bar"><div class="card-progress-fill"></div></div>
        <div class="card-progress-label">2 of 6 lessons complete</div>
        <div style="margin-top:18px;">
          <div class="card-lesson-item">
            <div class="card-lesson-dot"></div>
            <span class="card-lesson-text">What Is Codependency, Really?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-lesson-item">
            <div class="card-lesson-dot"></div>
            <span class="card-lesson-text">The Caretaker Trap</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-lesson-item">
            <div class="card-lesson-dot empty"></div>
            <span class="card-lesson-text muted">Other-Focus: The Core Symptom</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card hero-card-float">
        <div class="card-eyebrow">Reflection prompt</div>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--dark-text);line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;">"Whose emotional state am I most aware of right now?"</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="social-proof-bar">
    <div class="spb-avatars">
      <div class="spb-avatar">S</div>
      <div class="spb-avatar">M</div>
      <div class="spb-avatar">J</div>
      <div class="spb-avatar">R</div>
    </div>
    <p class="spb-text"><strong>Women breaking the pattern.</strong> More join every week.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
    <div class="section-title">Real lessons.<br>At your own pace.</div>
    <p class="section-sub">No fluff, no 15-minute video modules, no "journaling prompts" that pretend to be therapy. Just clear writing about what's actually happening and why.</p>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">📖</div>
        <h3>Structured modules</h3>
        <p>Each module covers one thing: what it is, why it happens, what to do. Written to be read once and actually understood.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌿</div>
        <h3>Go at your speed</h3>
        <p>Your progress saves automatically. Come back in a day or a month and you're exactly where you left off. No account needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🧭</div>
        <h3>Built for the beginning</h3>
        <p>Module 1 is about recognition. Seeing it clearly before trying to change anything. That's the only real starting point.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials — identity-shift stories from the community -->
  <section class="testimonials-section">
    <div class="testimonials-header">
      <div class="section-label">Stories from people breaking the pattern</div>
      <div class="section-title">They didn't know it had a name.</div>
      <p class="section-sub">Real moments from people working through the same patterns.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p class="tc-before">I used to rehearse every text before I sent it — rewriting it four or five times so nobody could possibly be upset with me. If someone didn't reply in an hour, I'd spiral.</p>
        <p class="tc-shift">"I learned that their silence isn't my emergency. I can sit with not knowing. That's what freedom actually feels like."</p>
        <div class="tc-outcome">Last week I sent a text, put my phone down, and went for a walk. Didn't check it for two hours.</div>
        <div class="tc-author">
          <div class="tc-author-avatar">S</div>
          <div><div class="tc-author-name">Sarah, 29</div><div class="tc-author-detail">Completed Module 1</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
